title: I moved the server transfer it doesn't work.
body: I applied for a transfer to server NA from Oceania two days ago. But it doesn't work properly and stays on the Oceania server. I don't know why. If you keep doing this, I want a refund my Oceania account server.

replies.body:
As per the server status, there are currently issues with account transfers: https://status.leagueoflegends.com/?en_AU#oce

Depending on the depth of the issue, player support may be able to help you, or offer you some more information on a timeline: https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new
